DITROPAN XL速 must be swallowed whole with the aid of liquids, and must not be chewed, divided, or crushed.
DITROPAN XL速 may be administered with or without food.
The recommended starting dose of DITROPAN XL速 is 5 or 10 mg once daily at approximately the same time each day. Dosage may be adjusted in 5-mg increments to achieve a balance of efficacy and tolerability (up to a maximum of 30 mg/day). In general, dosage adjustment may proceed at approximately weekly intervals.
